Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fs42\fad(300,300)}{\move(720,60,720,8)}{\blur3}字幕重校、压制：巴洛克哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油吧 阿兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊修巴尔野狗的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马尔科先生会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是先待在大总统那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们又能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中央图书馆?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马尔科先生居然把资料藏在军队的眼皮底下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fn方正隶变_GBK\b1\pos(720,890)\fs60}真相中的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 这个对大佐他们也要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底能不能信任那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西 就需要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}失却的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要急急忙忙上路?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得知斯卡在东城里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都突然开始担心中央的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给你添麻烦了 不过我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之前先进行处分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}处分?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我虽然知道结晶之炼金术师在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}却置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是想要把他保护起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然他的直属上司格兰反对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}研究成果被投入战场的事让他很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许为时已晚但现在我想补偿他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 那个研究…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以后也靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝您一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这样 什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是处分一下才能让你认真点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是个毫无破绽可寻的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破坏继而创造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请让我华丽地把你修好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把灵魂附着在盔甲上的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道它的只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是钢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为此必须先修好我这条胳膊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用不了炼金术的爱德华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是个爱抬杠的小鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 我要去我的整备师那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大佐你认识的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在那里看到过一个无能的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为太痛而哭爹喊娘的样子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"好疼! 好疼啊!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"尿裤子了啊!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}修好了以后准备干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去图书馆查一些资料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好长的旅程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说 我也得跟着大总统一行回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是不能离开这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要监督他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可没有信心对着那危险人物还能保护这两个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以下同上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}显而易见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一路上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就由我来护卫你们两位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们身体那样子 要是再被斯卡袭击怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一个人也没法子运送阿尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小孩子就该听大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然说我是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 你也说两句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 变成这样的身体后我是头一次被人当小孩对待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始收拾行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}变成这样的身体后我是头一次被当成行李对待…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 买份报纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去、去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}罗伊托我带话来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大佐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"因为事后处理会很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以不要死在我的管辖区里啊"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帮我转告他"我绝对不会死得比你早 臭大佐"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顺便说一下 把这位保镖带走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道你从马尔科那儿听到了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年前 被炼成合成兽的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的尸体后来被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那种破坏的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们已经查明是跟斯卡的炼金术一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样我就有足够理由跟他交手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在中央再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我帮你申请第一分馆的阅览许可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用了左手 不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中央的 中央的第一…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中央图书馆 第一分馆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大总统…大总统的答复怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你把藏资料的地点告诉那孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子离贤者之石又近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 如果资料上写了多余的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就不好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}读了它的话 你们就休想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以在那之前 我要稍微检查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我死了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像传言一样 你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格拉特尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你告诉那孩子的藏资料的地方在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真受不了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个大叔一直喋喋不休的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且还是对自己的家族吹个没完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也该稍微让我休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔? 阿尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔? 阿尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔在上一站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被搞错 卸下车了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们在下一站坐回程车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可等不及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别拦我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷静点 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我这件盔甲就算说"不是这里"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也只会把人吓死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥不知道有没有发现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想哭的是我才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他一个人还能到哪去!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那的确是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的盔甲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你画得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我们家代代相传的肖像画术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还磨蹭些什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}急什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们根本不明白我们的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从马尔科医生那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在伊修巴尔发生的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你看见车站站台上的盔甲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道什么人拿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常大 黑色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一等!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一等!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是手脚齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪会受这种罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离车站越来越远了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是幻听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这个盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全不疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请不要吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我是最新型的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中央那里很流行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能说话的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开关在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 你要去哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打架?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我大哥在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是想要变得像他一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就得能干出一两件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我就说"我要打赢一直和我们争地盘的达姆沙一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给你们看看"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这件事能成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就不会再有人把我当小孩看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家就会把我看作是大哥的左右手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干吧 干吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莫非 你是要去杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是个好盔甲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就算被枪打中也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才要穿着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为不会疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要自己不疼 就能随心所欲地打了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 应该会疼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么 你是次品么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心一定很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是 连心都不会疼比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手不要用力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是盔甲之诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不对…是诅咒之盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我合为一体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身心都不再会感觉到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永远 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子跟我这老头子相依为命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对之后要怎么办 她好像已经有了自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样就能让叔叔好过 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能看上了这个眼光也真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它不能给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是方便的话 我把制造它的技师介绍给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然嘴巴不饶人 不过技术不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}承蒙好意 不过我不需要义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}习惯了的话会方便很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能是这样 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我想让腿就这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在战场上受了刀伤 伤口腐烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}运到后方的时候 只能切掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}战场…你原来是军人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪里的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北方的? 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莫非是伊修巴尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在战场上不管是谁都会变得不像人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多残酷的任务都可以无动于衷地执行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道内心为了保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把感情都封闭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 战争一结束 就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那里的所见和所为都无法忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到这伤 马上就能回忆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以…所以才不要机械铠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不只是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我失去了一条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 因而获得了比它宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心中的平和与跟孙辈们一起的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人只有有所失才能有所得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也有人上了战场也不会有所触动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是所谓的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些人也失去了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算眼睛看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你既然已经有所失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该也已经得到了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炼金术里把这个叫等价交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没这回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我失去了右臂和左腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我弟弟失去了整个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了夺回那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们拼命地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夺回一切 那就是我们的梦想!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而 什么东西都没有得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都被夺走了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夺回一切的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 如果梦想实现了你又要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}实现了的梦想不能说是真正的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使如此 我们还是要夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是哥哥 哥哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 你身上都是羊臊味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系 到了皮纳可婆婆那里让她给我洗一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}四年前 大佐他来过利森普尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是偶然看到了我们寄出的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还说是在找我们的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 如果大佐他是去婆婆那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:22:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好 错过那趟车的话就要在这等到明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抓好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看我的家族代代相传负重跑步法!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要散架了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第十七集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有家人在等待的家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}踏上旅途的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们把房子烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们没有可以回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一直这么认为
